    <h2>Fire-Resistant Building Materials</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Concrete & Autoclaved Aerated Concrete (AAC):</strong> Durable and fire-resistant.</li>
        <li><strong>Gypsum-Based Products:</strong> Non-combustible and fireproof.</li>
        <li><strong>GigaCrete:</strong> Non-toxic and highly fire-resistant.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Fire-Resilient Design Principles</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Defensible Space:</strong> Clear vegetation and flammable materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Fire-Resistant Roofing & Siding:</strong> Use metal roofing and fiber-cement siding.</li>
        <li><strong>Protected Openings:</strong> Install double-pane tempered glass and ember-resistant vents.</li>
    </ul>

